{"tid":1800306,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警世】有樣嘢大家都唔肯做就齊齊投入大灣區","createTime":"2019-12-27T16:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T16:38:41.000Z","uid":137109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb781309eea8a85d60b2f1f34b861ba55f394fce","tid":1800306,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">防止中共愚民成功</span></span>，將佢套維穩觀念滲透係香港每一角落。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔反擊，更多人會愚昧相信謊言，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足同真相會被邊緣化</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n試諗下黃絲如何煉成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係<br />\n(1) 接收中立／客觀資訊；真相建立於客觀事實+持平觀點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2) 身邊人Carry；幸運嘅係父母，朋友、同學／老師一定有啟蒙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(3) 識得思考，而唔係人云亦云<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（一句概括所有藍絲=蠢人其實係一種Fundamental attribution error；美國曾經有個風暴，雖然預先疏散民眾，但仍然有批人冇走到，事後傷亡慘重。大部分民眾覺得呢批人都係『愚蠢』、『固執』、『懶』，但事實上有啲因為其他原因 eg. 接受唔到正確資訊、無能力離開、無錢／社交網絡係主因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMessage係唔好一竹篙打一船人而偷懶唔去Recruit其他人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入門版：<br />\n(1)：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新聞時段唔睇CCTVB係基本消費</span></span>。Subscribe 咗有線／Now未？每個月100蚊就可以防CCTVB洗腦，有線仲有埋Apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆必需UPDATE 『CCTVB不會告訴你的事』<br />\n(2)：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">從家族藍絲入手</span></span>，打下親情牌、尊重牌、故事牌（故事/Narratives比Hard Facts更易說服人)。Unlike咗佢啲藍Page。<br />\n(3)：需要耐性培養。善用歸謬法指出佢嘅荒謬；姐係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以子之矛攻子之盾</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neg. 假設佢「破壞公物」好暴力，再同佢講打細路、扑爆頭。接落去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一邊嘅武力係改變不公義嘅制度，一邊嘅暴力係維護不公義嘅蔓延</span></span><br />\n<br />\n進階版：<br />\n－公民覺醒，靠公民教育、論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n－Upgrade版蛇齋餅糉：利用你嘅知識／資源，借用區議會嘅平台，令社區有正面變化，突顯正苦無能。 (eg. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">識音樂巴絲搞吓concert，醫護巴絲做下Health Check</span></span>)<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS：極深藍真係唔好晒時間，呢啲等換血。但千祈唔可以當呢個係藉口，懶去說服轉軚。<br />\n記住民意64比，姐係話每說服到一個人轉軚，此消彼長下就會變<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壓倒性民意</span></strong>。<br />\nPS2：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線手足已經付出咗好多，和理非除咗唔割席其實應該做Backup角色</span>，令受影響嘅人都理解呢場抗爭。以前和你飛我哋會同旅客say sorry，依家都可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>解釋運動背後理念，注重返運動嘅正當性，唔好只側重警暴</ins></span></strong></span>。"},{"pid":"b944be4b53060f494213a77a1230efde8aa6d810","tid":1800306,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"連登Post長文預咗冇乜人睇，僅有入嚟嘅麻煩幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c2288c122e2cc90dd8cc474a59877a87ad992d","tid":1800306,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"push 1/10"},{"pid":"0e7a0ea5e98beec7a59c85ecb2b17849be07dbf3","tid":1800306,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"push 2/10"},{"pid":"937e3ac50e9842781ec44ea4a745f8092c869d76","tid":1800306,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799015</a><br />\n<br />\n你地又話好討厭甴近平既.....<